ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Series of speakers related to clinical psychology. Highly recommend.
I'd definitely recommend Psyc720 to other grad and undergrad students interested in research related to clinical psychology.

I would definitely recommend this course to other students interested in the current ongoing research in clinical psychology. It is a great way to get acquainted with the interests of potential collaborators.
Very interesting lunch meeting where many leading experts of the field are invited as guest speakers.I would recommend it.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Provides broad information about the field of clinical psych.
While there were no presentations that addressed my particular interests, I definitely have a deeper knowledge of the other research occurring in the area of clinical psychology.
